{"tid":1544170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要人！要人！秀茂坪商場有放映會 藍屍廢老重地","createTime":"2019-09-05T12:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T08:17:45.000Z","uid":24265,"like":159,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"2093eb4faafbe2fd06af3c20ffedbea69f58f22f","tid":1544170,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uh8FpLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUh8FpLA.jpg&h=a5e63cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n快啲出黎呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84524c64df7943bd128fe54f1a0012a3e9b0a048","tid":1544170,"uid":9049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:49:03.000Z","msg":"各地區連儂牆要人，文宣大量要人<br />\n解釋清楚！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全民抗爭，長久戰、拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗<br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少使用八達通<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點咆哮！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests #Chinazi<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWMg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=8148fc9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著將呢段訊息copy and paste嚟推post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 每星期做孝子，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股、少掂中港股票<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.05"},{"pid":"f10128ed5c8123ec1871b14abcaffe9b7a4da18f","tid":1544170,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:49: