\n遊行唔係淨係星期六日，全民GEAR!<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n【和理非】反對黨鐵助紂為虐 - 全民Gear搭地鐵活動開始!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0f5fa87d61720165ed44fbd532c642434fe2d396","tid":1544170,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:24:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e42f91d5c71255ec8c02a1c55b71beb8d0f625c6","tid":1544170,"uid":143371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:24:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13241a6a36b4b427dec00387731ee4c80ad5a217","tid":1544170,"uid":148980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:25:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd83f07487d58341d8914fb7e1f3e4b9a27733ec","tid":1544170,"uid":143371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2093eb4faafbe2fd06af3c20ffedbea69f58f22f","tid":1544170,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uh8FpLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUh8FpLA.jpg&h=a5e63cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n快啲出黎呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:25:20.000Z","msg":"Btw可唔可以影下個mon後面點企 學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe448d548bf1437932e75330e8dd5182bb34e6a","tid":1544170,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd83f07487d58341d8914fb7e1f3e4b9a27733ec","tid":1544170,"uid":143371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2093eb4faafbe2fd06af3c20ffedbea69f58f22f","tid":1544170,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uh8FpLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUh8FpLA.jpg&h=a5e63cb5&